      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i think something is actually wrong with my eyes or something... i was driving to work today and i swear i saw the exact same grey sedan pass me three times in a row. like not just a similar car, but the same dent on the bumper and everything. and then the light hit the trees in a way that looked... i dont know, pixelated? like the lighting engine couldnt keep up. has anyone else ever seen stuff like that?",
